And Paul is writing in Romans beginning at chapter 1 and verse 16. He says,

00:04:37.504 --> 00:04:39.552
For I am not ashamed.

00:04:39.392 --> 00:04:42.528
Of this good news about Christ,

00:04:42.432 --> 00:04:45.152
It is the power of God at work.

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:47.392
Sleeping everyone who believes.

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:50.080
The Jew first and the Gentile.

00:04:50.848 --> 00:04:54.880
This good news tells us how God makes us right.

00:04:54.784 --> 00:04:56.256
In his sight.

00:04:57.088 --> 00:04:59.840
This was accomplished from start to finish

00:05:00.192 --> 00:05:01.184
Five.

